<i>with her best friend.</i>

21:11.312 --> 21:12.980
<i>I know it’s terrible, but</i>

21:12.980 --> 21:14.607
<i>I didn’t mean it</i>
<i>to end up like...</i>

21:14.607 --> 21:16.192
